data.Name: I
data.Description: Linked to FacetType direction: Indicates that the property is aligned with the I axis. For instance permeability in the I direction.

data.Name: J
data.Description: Linked to FacetType direction: Indicates that the property property is aligned with the J axis. For instance permeability in the J direction.

data.Name: K
data.Description: Linked to FacetType direction: Indicates that the  property is aligned with the K axis. For instance vertical permeability (along K).

data.Name: X
data.Description: Linked to FacetType direction: Indicates that the property is defined along X direction.

data.Name: Y
data.Description: Linked to FacetType direction: Indicates that the property is defined along Y direction.

data.Name: Z
data.Description: Linked to FacetType direction: Indicates that the property  is defined along Z direction.

data.Name: I+
data.Description: Linked to FacetType direction: Indicates that the property is directional along I direction for a reservoir grid (along increasing I values)

data.Name: J+
data.Description: Linked to FacetType direction: Indicates that the property is directional along J direction for a reservoir grid (along increasing J values)

data.Name: K+
data.Description: Linked to FacetType direction: Indicates that the property is directional along K direction for a reservoir grid (along increasing K values)

data.Name: X+

data.Name: Z+

data.Name: net
